Tacium Poker API 1.0.0

Apache 2.0

The communication betweeen Tacium Poker Clinet and Tacium Poker Server.

number

number

The big blind amount.

integer

A number that indicates the players seat on the table.

  • 0 - no seat
  • 1 - left most seat
  • 2 - the seat to the right of seat 1
  • etc.

integer

A number that indicates the players seat on the table.

  • 0 - no seat
  • 1 - left most seat
  • 2 - the seat to the right of seat 1
  • etc.

cards Cards
object
public
object
flop
array<string>

Items:

0 Card
string

2 characters string representing a card. Each card is composed of a Rank [23456789JTQKA] and a Suit [shdc]. Examples:

  • 'As' is Ace pf spades.
  • '8h' is the Eight of hearts.

A unique card is '--' which represents the card's back (a hidden card). An empty string, or null card, means no card.

Additional items are allowed.

    "game": {

      "small_blind": 100,
      "big_blind": 200,
      "button_seat": 3,
      "hero_seat": 3
    },
    "scene": {
      "background": "scenes/12345678",
      "table": "tables/12345678",
      "deck": "decks/12345678"
    },
    "players_info": [
      {
        "seat": 3,
        "name": "John",
        "avatar": "avatars/12345678",
        "cerebo": "cerebos/12345678"
      }
    ],
    "players_state": {
      "next_player": {
        "seat": 3,
        "time": 5
      },
      "state": [
        {
          "seat": 3,
          "active": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "cards": {
      "public": {
        "flop": [
          "As",
          "Ks",
          "Qs"
        ],
        "turn": [
          "Js"
        ],
        "river": [
          "Ts"
        ]
      },
      "private": [
        {
          "seat": 3,
          "cards": [
            "2h",
            "7d"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "chips": {
      "pot": 120,
      "side_pots": [
        40
      ],
      "table_sum": 30,
      "stacks": [
        {
          "seat": 3,
          "sum": 100
        }
      ],
      "wagers": [
        {
          "seat": 3,
          "sum": 100
        }
      ],
      "collects": [
        {
          "seat": 3,
          "sum": 100,
          "collect_type": "win"
        }
      ]
    },
    "actions": [
      {
        "seat": 3,
        "action": {
          "type": "Raise",
          "sum": 100,
          "fold": true,
          "allin": true
        }
      }
    ],
    "reactions": [
      {
        "seat": 3,
        "reaction": "Win"
      }
    ],
    "events": [
      "NewGame"
    ],
    "hero": {
      "time": 5,
      "allowed_actions": [
        {
          "type": "Raise",
          "default_sum": 100,
          "min_sum": 100,
          "max_sum": 100
        }
      ],
      "suggested_action": {
        "type": "Raise",
        "sum": 100
      }
    }
  }
}
